    • getTextAt

      public java.lang.String getTextAt​(java.lang.String text, java.lang.String indexSymbol)
      Get substring in text. 3 options: see for more info @param indexSymbol.
      Parameters:
      text - Gets substring from text.
      indexSymbol - Get substring between Symbol and last ":". If indexSymbol = ":". THEN get substring after last ":". If indexSymbol = "". THEN get everything before ":"
      Returns:
      Substring in text or "".
